This repository provides self-hosted usage analytics for Claude Code via
OpenTelemetry. It does not vendor third-party source, but its Helm bundle
(deploy-templates/) declares dependencies on, and its local testbed
(local/docker-compose.yaml) runs, upstream software that remains under its own
license in its own upstream project:

  - OpenTelemetry Collector (Contrib) - Apache-2.0 - https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-collector-contrib
  - Prometheus                        - Apache-2.0 - https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus
  - Grafana Loki                      - AGPL-3.0   - https://github.com/grafana/loki
  - Grafana                           - AGPL-3.0   - https://github.com/grafana/grafana

These components are pulled at deploy/run time from their upstream registries and
Helm repositories; they are NOT redistributed by this repository. Please consult
each project for its own license terms.
